The '''Lythian pirates''' were a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] gang from the [[Lythia system/Legends|Lythia system]] that [[Lythian pirate raids|raided]] [[Jabiim/Legends|Jabiim]] in the years before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. The [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] did nothing to stop their depredations against the [[Jabiimi]] people.

